'''貝特拉姆卡別墅'''（Muzeum W.A. Mozarta a manželů Duškových）是位於[[捷克|捷克]]首都[[布拉格|布拉格]]市內的一座建築，[[莫扎特|莫扎特]]曾經到訪過這裡。現在貝特拉姆卡別墅是一座以莫扎特為主體的博物館<ref>{{cite book|title=Travel Prague: Illustrated City Guide, Phrasebook, and Maps|year=2007|publisher=MobileReference|isbn=9781605010243|url=http://books.google.com.au/books?id=A9eD6XX7NjoC&lpg=PT161&ots=neZGmuCjFw&dq=it+was+purchased+by+Lambert+Popelka+who+was+a+great+admirer+of+Mozart&pg=PT161&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=it%20was%20purchased%20by%20Lambert%20Popelka%20who%20was%20a%20great%20admirer%20of%20Mozart&f=false|access-date=2015-10-11|archive-date=2014-01-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102221949/http://books.google.com.au/books?id=A9eD6XX7NjoC&lpg=PT161&ots=neZGmuCjFw&dq=it+was+purchased+by+Lambert+Popelka+who+was+a+great+admirer+of+Mozart&pg=PT161&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=it%20was%20purchased%20by%20Lambert%20Popelka%20who%20was%20a%20great%20admirer%20of%20Mozart&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
